{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji2","name":"毛泽东全集第2卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji2.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给彭璜的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给彭璜的信！]"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1921年1月6日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兄一月来对礼容态度，我颇不满意，大违兄平日恢恢之度，礼容即万不当，亦不宜以此非人世所堪之意态对之，面誉人与面毁人同非人世所堪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年团拟于一月十三日开成立会，望参加。[1]这是毛泽东致彭璜信的主要内容。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1921,"month":1,"day":6}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":374,"page_end":374},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}